data.description: Nestled in the charming neighborhood of Moody TX, this stunning property located at 119 Ave B! Built in 2021, this 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home boasts a cozy and inviting atmosphere, perfect for creating lasting memories. Step inside to discover a spacious and open floor plan, providing the perfect balance between comfort and functionality. Natural light floods the living space, illuminating the details and finishes throughout. As you make your way towards the heart of the home, you'll be greeted by a well-appointed kitchen, ideal for culinary enthusiasts with ample counter space and storage. But it's not just the interior that will captivate you. Step outside and be greeted by a big backyard, perfect for entertaining guests or simply relaxing with a good book. Tucked away in a peaceful cul de sac, privacy and tranquility are yours to enjoy. Don't let the words "cozy" and "small" deceive you - this property offers an ample amount of space for all your needs. Whether it's a quiet evening at home or a lively social gathering, this home has it all. So why wait? Don't miss the opportunity to make this charming property your forever home. Schedule a viewing today and make your dreams a reality!
